problem_text_en: As shown in the figure, A and B are two points on ⊙O, AC is the tangent of ⊙O, ∠B = N_0, then ∠BAC = ()
raw_answer: 解:∵A、B是⊙O上的两点,∴OA=OB,∴∠OAB=∠B=65°,∵AC是⊙O的切线；∴∠OAC=90°,∴∠BAC=∠OAC-∠OAB=90°-65°=25°．故选:B．
